{"tid":339350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【身體卻很誠實】唔返內地唔留港 梁美芬訪美考察一國兩制","createTime":"2017-07-29T03:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T05:59:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a0f928ecc89a5de580e48ffcc324fd5c04e2cb","tid":339350,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】經民聯立法會議員梁美芬本身係城大法律學者，擅長研究《基本法》，而呢個暑假佢話好忙，要再研習一國兩制，但佢唔喺香港或內地研習，而係走去美國路易斯安那州（Louisana），考察當地嘅「一國兩制」！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">梁美芬同Emily講，8月份會好長時間唔喺香港，先會去美國探仔，然後一家人會參加加勒比郵輪團旅行。</span>不過，佢之後會留喺路易斯安那州大概兩個禮拜做學術交流，佢獲當地機構邀請去考察同發表演講，題目係「Hybridity of common law and civil law : Hong Kong Practice」，大意係指香港係行獨特嘅一國兩制，法制行普通法，但一國就行大陸法制度。梁美芬話，路易斯安那州其實都係一個好特別嘅法制地區，同法國有歷史淵源，係美國唯一保留大陸法嘅州份。佢仲話多年前已經帶過一批內地法官去當地考察，而今次佢再去美國，想留長啲時間，觀摩埋當地法院點樣審案。<br />\n<br />\n近期香港社會討論一國兩制，梁美芬之前就利用呢個題目，寫咗篇學術文章刊登喺學術期刊，評論一地兩檢衍生嘅各項法律爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170729/s00002/1501264233842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170729%2Fs00002%2F1501264233842&d=zD9qubVoP8tvnCVHFqtzmW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=e7b7716b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170729%2Fs00002%2F1501264233842&h=caa416d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170729/s00002/1501264233842</a>"},{"pid":"d6e66fa4f33bc7365c72e677598ab0e55364f654","tid":339350,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b53da2d98cd407207bfc06270c51e54f556a48","tid":339350,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ac353e8d68c04feb85961dd7dc6a1917371f93","tid":339350,"uid":76349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:55:07.000Z","msg":"拿！美帝咪撚比佢入境呀，共牒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71dd89efaa6e31399265df5ae2e1661b81bf59a","tid":339350,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}